#

Pineapple Guacamole

10 min
$5
150 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

vegetariangluten-freedairy-free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Appetizer

Tags:

appetizersnackeasy

Description

A tropical twist on traditional guacamole, this Pineapple Guacamole is fresh, zesty, and perfect for dipping or as a topping.

Ingredients

  • ripe avocados: 2
  • fresh pineapple, diced: 1 cup
  • lime, juiced: 1
  • red onion, finely chopped: 1/4 cup
  • cilantro, chopped: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
